=== Transitive verb ===
'''brush'''

#<!--DefTV-A-->To clean with a brush.
#: ''Brush your teeth.''
#<!--DefTV-B-->To untangle or arrange with a brush.
#: ''Brush your hair.''
#<!--DefTV-C-->To apply with a brush.
#: ''Brush the paint onto the walls.''
#<!--DefTV-D-->To remove with a sweeping motion.
#: ''Brush the flour off your clothes.''
